query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 acc q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 5 AND q1.favorite_count <= 5000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('audio',
'ggplot2',
'selenium',
'spring-mvc',
'tensorflow',
'terminal')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow',
'superuser')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Analytical',
'Archaeologist',
'Booster',
'Cleanup',
'Deputy',
'Documentation User',
'Electorate',
'Great Question',
'Investor',
'Not a Robot',
'Outspoken',
'Talkative',
'Taxonomist',
'Unsung Hero');
